data.description: Enjoy all of the character of this turn of the century home with updated features you can't help but enjoy.  The cove ceiling, original wood work, and large living spaces offer the charm of the past with new carpet, stainless steel appliances and finished basement that bring this home into the comfort of the modern era.  The first floor master is perfect for avoiding the stairs and the fully fenced yard offers the oasis of privacy for your outdoor activities, entertaining or relaxing everyday getaway.
